{"tid":1953978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男旅客走私57隻瀕危野生陸龜囚兩年　獸醫指陸龜受不必要痛楚！","createTime":"2020-04-01T13:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T14:00:29.000Z","uid":63113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c37f402ba6123194cd31226b5a6115ed5e614170","tid":1953978,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b4d49944f3933b81f33381531202644c4bc5ce","tid":1953978,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:18:52.000Z","msg":"一名旅客因走私57隻陸龜，違反《保護瀕危動植物物種條例》及《防止殘酷對待動物條例》，被判罪名成立，判監24個月，是有關條例歷來非法進口瀕危活生動物最高的刑罰。<br />\n<br />\n漁護署表示，47歲男旅客從科摩羅莫洛尼經埃塞俄比亞阿迪斯阿貝巴，於去年9月28日抵達本港。海關人員在行李內發現57隻被膠紙綑綁的陸龜，包括55隻輻紋陸龜和兩隻馬達加斯加陸龜。<br />\n<br />\n漁護署獸醫跟進檢驗後，表示這57隻陸龜受到不必要的痛苦，健康和福利被嚴重忽視。漁護署之後檢控該名男子。他於前日在區域法院被判罪名成立。法院分別就《保護瀕危動植物物種條例》及《防止殘酷對待動物條例》以36個月及12個月為量刑起點，因被告認罪，扣減三分之一刑期，判被告即時監禁24個月及8個月，同期執行。<br />\n<br />\n輻紋陸龜和馬達加斯加陸龜屬《瀕危野生動植物種國際貿易公約》附錄的列明物種，受條例規管。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518289-20200401.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518289-20200401.htm&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnfPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=40798af6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518289-20200401.htm&h=d9de7f59\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518289-20200401.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ffcff4bd6f2a54d7fc95e3eca00a625d29061cad","tid":1953978,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wQxEoy5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQxEoy5.jpg&h=3a987664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHVRY7D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHVRY7D.jpg&h=e823d671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />